  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK561">
<l>takkāṅku nāṭit talaiccellā vaṇṇattā </l>
<l>lottāṅ koṟuppatu vēntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is a king who having equitably examined (any injustice which has been brought to his notice), suitably punishes it, so that it may not be again committed.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
